      "rationale": "Primary QoI is the relative hemolysis index RH, which is the direct COU decision quantity. Supporting QoIs (head-flow curve, wall shear stress distribution) are mechanistically linked to hemolysis via the Giersiepen power-law model. Relevance chain documented in the credibility assessment report."
