    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out under MRL 2 provisions with documented justification. Validation results demonstrate head-flow error of 3.2% (threshold 5%), RH < 1.0 for all operating conditions, and PIV velocity NRMSD of 6.1% (threshold 10%). The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Submission to FDA 510(k) pathway authorized.",
